"title": "1240: God, the Rock",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "1240: god, the rock",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>An OT title for God and a Messianic title signifying that God's people can rely on him for absolute protection and salvation.</p>\n<h2>Rock as a title for Israel's God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:35\">PSA 78:35</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen49:24\">GEN 49:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:15\">DEU 32:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:18\">DEU 32:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:30\">DEU 32:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam23:3\">2SA 23:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps42:9\">PSA 42:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa30:29\">ISA 30:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab1:12\">HAB 1:12</a></p>\n<h2>God the Rock is unique</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam22:32\">2SA 22:32</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps18:31\">PSA 18:31</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam2:2\">1SA 2:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa44:8\">ISA 44:8</a></p>\n<h2>The Rock is superior to other gods</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:31\">DEU 32:31</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:37\">DEU 32:37</a></p>\n<h2>The Rock is worthy to be praised</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps144:1\">PSA 144:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:4\">DEU 32:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps92:15\">PSA 92:15</a></p>\n<h2>God the Rock and his people</h2>\n<h3>God the Rock is a refuge for his people</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps62:7\">PSA 62:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps28:1\">PSA 28:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps31:1-Ps31:3\">PSA 31:1–31:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps61:2\">PSA 61:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps71:3\">PSA 71:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa26:4\">ISA 26:4</a></p>\n<h3>God the Rock is his people's fortress</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps94:22\">PSA 94:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps28:8\">PSA 28:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps46:7\">PSA 46:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps46:11\">PSA 46:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps48:3\">PSA 48:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps59:9\">PSA 59:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps59:16-Ps59:17\">PSA 59:16–59:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps91:2\">PSA 91:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps144:2\">PSA 144:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer16:19\">JER 16:19</a></p>\n<h3>God the Rock is his people's security</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam22:3\">2SA 22:3</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps18:2\">PSA 18:2</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps9:9\">PSA 9:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps27:1\">PSA 27:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps37:39\">PSA 37:39</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps43:2\">PSA 43:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps52:7\">PSA 52:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel3:16\">JOL 3:16</a></p>\n<h3>God the Rock saves and delivers his people</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps95:1\">PSA 95:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam22:47\">2SA 22:47</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps18:46\">PSA 18:46</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps19:14\">PSA 19:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps62:2\">PSA 62:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps89:26\">PSA 89:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa17:10\">ISA 17:10</a></p>\n<h2>Rock as a Messianic title</h2>\n<h3>The Messiah is the rock/stone on which God's living temple stands</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa8:14\">ISA 8:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa28:16\">ISA 28:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps118:22\">PSA 118:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:42\">MAT 21:42</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:10\">MRK 12:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke20:17\">LUK 20:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:11\">ACT 4:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:6-1Pet2:7\">1PE 2:6–2:7</a></p>\n<h3>The Messiah's kingdom is eternal and immovable like a rock</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan2:34-Dan2:35\">DAN 2:34–2:35</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan2:44-Dan2:45\">DAN 2:44–2:45</a></p>\n<h3>Consequences of rejecting the rock/stone</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:44\">MAT 21:44</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke20:18\">LUK 20:18</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom9:32-Rom9:33\">ROM 9:32–9:33</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:4-1Pet2:8\">1PE 2:4–2:8</a></p>",
